<text id="138580">An academic who walks the Lands Between, and a member of the School of Hierodas who seeks knowledge through travel. He contracted a disease that causes abnormally rapid aging.

Boasts impressive arcane levels but other attributes suffer. Has the potential to gain incredible battlefield advantages through observation.

Preference: Thrusting swords</text>
